title: Resonance Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Fusion
description: Cafe and concert venue where the food served is vegan; dairy milk is an option for the large selection of coffee and tea. Has free Wi-Fi, live music nightly. Meals range from gluten-free soups to sandwiches (BLT, breakfast sandwich with scrambled tofu) to rice bowls. Everything is made-in-house, including the kimchi. Not wheelchair friendly, as there are five stairs at the door. If you call ahead, you could be let in through the back door which has one stair. Child friendly with a change table and several high chairs.
